name: I See Faces Morphing in the Clouds (Or: Psilocybin and Your Daily Dose of Atmosphere)
description: Tune in and tune out. You only have one place to be and that is here. Present. Omnipresent. Omniscient, ubiquitous. There are many names, all fluid, all around us. How marvelous it is to marvel! What have we here? Can you hear me over there? Float into it; meld with it. Be it. We are.
